Chaz Bono and fiancée Jennifer Elia have called off their engagement.

The couple - who have dated since 1999 - have not only cancelled plans to get hitched but have decided to end their relationship entirely.

His spokesperson Howard Bragman said today: ‘They leave this relationship with great love, respect and affection toward one another.

'No further amplification will be forthcoming and they ask that you respect their privacy at this time.'

